quran[24{c,v,t}:
37,1,qasam hai saf bandhnay walon ki para jama kar
37,2,phir dantnay walon ki jhirak kar
37,3,phir zikar ( yani quran ) parhnay walon ki ( ghhor krkr )
37,4,ke tumhara mabood aik hai
37,5,jo asmano aur zameen aur jo cheeze un mein hain sab ka maalik hai aur Sooraj ke tulu honay ke maqamat ka bhi maalik hai
37,6,be shak hum hi ne aasman duniya ko sitaron ki zeenat se muzayyankiya
37,7,aur har shetan sarkash se is ki hifazat ki
37,8,ke oopar ki majlis ki taraf kaan nah lgaskin aur har taraf se ( un par angare ) phainky jatay hain
37,9,( yani wahan se ) nikaal dainay ko aur un ke liye daimi azaab hai
37,10,haan jo koi ( firshton ki kisi baat ko ) chori se jhapat lena chahta hai to jalta howa angara un ke peechay lagta hai
37,11,to un se pucho ke un ka banana mushkil hai ya jitni khalqat hum ne banai hai? inhen hum ne chipaknay gaaray se banaya hai
37,12,haan tum to taajjub karte ho aur yeh tamaskhur karte hain
37,13,aur jab un ko nasiyaat di jati hai to nasiyaat qubool nahi karte
37,14,aur jab koi nishani dekhte hain to thathay karte hain
37,15,aur kehte hain ke yeh to Sarih jaadoo hai
37,16,bhala jab hum margaye aur matti aur haddiyan hogaye tokiya phir uthaye jayen ge ?
37,17,aurkiya hamaray baap dada bhi ( jo ) pehlay ( ho guzray hain )
37,18,keh do ke haan aur tum zaleel hogay
37,19,woh to aik zor ki aawaz hogi aur yeh is waqt dekhnay lagen ge
37,20,"aur kahin ge, haae shamat yahi jaza ka din hai"
37,21,( kaha jaye ga ke haan ) faislay ka din jis ko tum jhoot samajte they yahi hai
37,22,jo log zulm karte they un ko aur un ke hum jnson ko aur jin ko woh pooja karte they ( sab ko ) jama karlo
37,23,( yani jin ko ) khuda ke siwa ( pooja karte they ) phir un ko jahannum ke raste par chala do
37,24,aur un ko tehraye rakho ke un se ( kuch ) poochna hai
